{"tid":421150,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇睇左哈佬喂猛鬼戲院最終回嘅音樂達人","createTime":"2017-10-02T04:00:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-02T08:13:03.000Z","uid":39218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d6f430c5d7501b54d1db720eb0ab9cc0a23e81e6","tid":421150,"uid":39218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T04:00:26.000Z","msg":"個show幾好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n未睇嘅人黎緊可以去睇下<br />\n<br />\n其實開po係想問下有冇人知入面首Britney Spears嘅toxic嘅版本可以係邊度搵到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我淨係搵到一開頭嗰段仔應該係yael naim唱嘅版本黎，但後段就唔一樣，個show嘅版本係mix左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想睇下有冇高手可以搵到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果有需要，其實我搵到段片係錄左佢個show，但始終咁樣擺條片上黎，好似唔係幾尊重班表演者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如非必要都唔擺啦，或者加密放上黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c536e5f7e1c7903262744227be7903825050590","tid":421150,"uid":39218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T04:01:34.000Z","msg":"屌手殘，最尾個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />錯鳩左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"006954e9a2eb0dda77d25e23568ddaf91a992644","tid":421150,"uid":39218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T04:07:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9f9a74e97f893eadfa4ea61cc1d01401be7e057b","tid":421150,"uid":39218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T04:31:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推</blockquote>"},{"pid":"1250b94b89e8054cf889ab8438c0c0aa90bd853c","tid":421150,"uid":39218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T04:59:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18321feea57e2aa41fac757db69fd7c87a2c996b","tid":421150,"uid":39218,"like":